OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and isolated
OL,6,Fshowers, these most likely across
OL,7,Fwestern areas, until late afternoon.
OL,8,FThen frequent showers will spread
OL,9,Feast, locally heavy with a small
OL,10,Fchance of hail and thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers easing into the
OL,13,Fevening but remaining cloudy as a band
OL,14,Fof rain and showers moves in from the
OL,15,Fwest during the early hours, spreading
OL,16,Feastwards by the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
