OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FSunshine and scattered
OL,6,Fshowers, occasionally heavy. Cloud
OL,7,Fwill spread eastwards across the
OL,8,Fregion during the evening ahead of a
OL,9,Fband of rain and strong winds
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FTuesday breezy with frequent heavy
OL,14,Fshowers. Wednesday breezy, bright
OL,15,Fspells and isolated showers. Becoming
OL,16,Fsettled and dry on Thursday.
OL,17,FTemperatures normal or slightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
